me.fami6xx.rpuniverse.core.jobs

Class WorkingStep

  • java.lang.Object
    • me.fami6xx.rpuniverse.core.jobs.WorkingStep

  • public class WorkingStep
extends java.lang.Object
    A working step is a step that the player must do to receive an item. It can be set that the player must have a specific item in his inventory to do the step.
